ActivityNode.DisplayName: Set CP SIList Service Item Data

Configuration.DisplayName: Set CP SIList Service Item Data

XSLDocument.FormattedCode:
<?xml version="1.0"?> <xsl:stylesheet version="1.0" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform">
<!-- to find the CP/SOA pairs --> <xsl:key name='k1' match="row" use="UniqueID"/>
<xsl:template match="@* | node()"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:apply-templates select="@* | node()" /> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="results"> <xsl:copy> <!-- copy based on existence of the nsapi ID (CP) (it's an update) --> <xsl:apply-templates select="row[key('k1', UniqueID)[2]]" /> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="row"> <xsl:variable name="rowName" select="UniqueID" /> <xsl:copy> <!-- copy each element in the row... --> <xsl:for-each select="@*"> <xsl:copy/> </xsl:for-each> <xsl:apply-templates/> <!-- ...and the Status and Name fields from the nsapi (CP) list --> <xsl:apply-templates select="../row[UniqueID=$rowName and id-{0}='nsapi']/Status"/> <xsl:apply-templates select="../row[UniqueID=$rowName and id-{1}='nsapi']/FSMStatus"/> <!-- <xsl:apply-templates select="../row[UniqueID=$rowName and id-{2}='nsapi']/FirstDiscovered"/> --> <xsl:apply-templates select="../row[UniqueID=$rowName and id-{3}='nsapi']/Name"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<!-- skip copying the nsapi (CP) list records --> <xsl:template match="*[descendant-or-self::row[id-{4}='nsapi'] and parent::*]"/>
</xsl:stylesheet>

<?xml version="1.0"?> <xsl:stylesheet version="1.0" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform">
<!-- to find the CP/SOA pairs --> <xsl:key name='k1' match="row" use="UniqueID"/>
<xsl:template match="@* | node()"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:apply-templates select="@* | node()" /> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="results"> <xsl:copy> <!-- copy based on existence of the nsapi ID (CP) (it's an update) --> <xsl:apply-templates select="row[key('k1', UniqueID)[2]]" /> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="row"> <xsl:variable name="rowName" select="UniqueID" /> <xsl:copy> <!-- copy each element in the row... --> <xsl:for-each select="@*"> <xsl:copy/> </xsl:for-each> <xsl:apply-templates/> <!-- ...and the Status and Name fields from the nsapi (CP) list --> <xsl:apply-templates select="../row[UniqueID=$rowName and id-{0}='nsapi']/Name"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<!-- skip copying the nsapi (CP) list records --> <xsl:template match="*[descendant-or-self::row[id-{1}='nsapi'] and parent::*]"/>
</xsl:stylesheet>

</xsl:stylesheet>
